          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a small pan over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pine nut & seed mix</strong> and cook for 3-5 min or until they're toasted and darkened slightly in colour</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk so they don’t burn!</p>",
      "order": 5,
